summary: I believe healing in a nature way a best way. I am encouraged and facinated by Acupuncture every day. All kinds of my knowledges enrich my life and my work. Study is not a burden, it's fun. My interested subjects are many: acupuncture, herbal medicine, Chinese medicine classical books, all kinds of philosophy, religion. To heal a disease you need only medical techniques, to heal a person you need more wisdom. Traditional Chinese Medicine is a medicine full of wisdom.
